name: OS Hybrid Fitted, "Zachary", SECONDS
description:
One Size Hybrid Diaper with snap-in soaker system and fold down rise. FDR has two snaps to keep it folded helping to keep it from coming loose during wear. Two or three snaps on the wings (your preference), and cross-over capabilities. Legs are comfort turned. Hidden layer of polyester fleece acts as a slight barrier, pushing moisture back into the soaker. 8 layers of natural, highly absorbent materials. Requires a cover to be entire waterproof.

Shell

Outer: knit jersey, cotton or cotton blend
Core: blizzard polyester fleece 
Inner: cotton or bamboo velour

Soaker

1 layer of bamboo or cotton velour against baby's bum
2 layers of organic cotton Sherpa
2 layers of heavy organic bamboo fleece
1 layer of bamboo hemp fleece

This item has one tear that has been mended. It is entirely functional, just has this one flaw.
